<P align=justify>This service is part of your membership. We highly recommend that your listing include photos of your motorhome or other vehicle. You can include up to 2 photos. Maybe you would like to show the interior of your vehicle. Maybe one photo of the exterior is enough. After your listing is online you may upload an image at any time. You can attach your photo to an <A href="mailto:admin@MotorhomeExchange-Sell.com" target="">e-mail.</A> <FONT color=#0066cc><STRONG>&gt;&gt;&gt;</STRONG></FONT> Please send in the small JPG format. Please make sure that your image file is no bigger than 480 pixels. Please save at 72dpi-medium to high quality. Make sure your image files are no larger than 250kb. Alternatively you can send 1 or 2 photo’s to<FONT color=#ff6600> <STRONG><EM>MotorhomeExchange-Sell.com</EM></STRONG></FONT> PO Box 39119, Harewood, Christchurch, New Zealand. We will upload your photo for you, into your listing. <BR><FONT size=3><STRONG><BR><FONT color=#0066cc>This is part of your membership at</FONT> <EM><FONT color=#ff6600>MotorhomeExchange-Sell.com</FONT></EM></STRONG></FONT></P></FONT>
